http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/hall_of_fame/reagan/speech/in1.htm 204.71.237.74 19970109120715 text/html 15857
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 12:07:33 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 19-Dec-95 18:56:29 GMT
