<DOCOLDNO>IA055-000922-B042-217</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.cpac.org:80/townhall/columnists/schlafly/schl081795.html 204.71.237.74 19970109152314 text/html 5708
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
