http://www.cpac.org:80/heritage/library/categories/trade/bg999.html 204.71.237.74 19970109192701 text/html 45808
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Thursday, 09-Jan-97 19:26:48 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 23-Apr-96 01:32:58 GMT
Content-length: 45621
